<snippet>
	<description>void add - 加边，费用流</description>
	<content><![CDATA[void add(int a, int b, int c, int d)  // 添加一条边a->b，容量为c，费用为d；同时增加一条反向边
{
    e[idx] = b, f[idx] = c, w[idx] = d, ne[idx] = h[a], h[a] = idx ++ ;
    e[idx] = a, f[idx] = 0, w[idx] = -d, ne[idx] = h[b], h[b] = idx ++ ;
}
]]></content>
